# Breezy Rhino Website Recreation Plan

## Task Overview
Recreate the website found at https://www.awwwards.com/sites/breezy-rhino.

## Steps
- [x] Navigate to Awwwards page and click "Visit Site"
- [x] Analyze Color Scheme
- [x] Analyze Typography
- [x] Analyze Hero Section Layout
- [x] Analyze Subsequent Sections Layout
- [x] Analyze Animations and Interactions
- [x] Analyze Navbar and Footer
- [x] Compile final detailed report

## Findings
- **Color Palette**:
  - Black: #000000 (Main background, sections)
  - White: #FFFFFF (Text, secondary backgrounds)
  - Lime Green: #DFFF3B (Primary accent for CTAs and tags)
  - Light Grey: #F3F3F3 (Section backgrounds)
  - Sky Blue: #87CEEB (Footer pill background)
  - Orange: #F2994A (Misc cards)
- **Typography**:
  - Headings: Bold, Neo-Grotesk (Likely **PP Neue Montreal** or **General Sans**). Very tight tracking.
  - Huge Footer Text: Ultra-wide, heavy sans-serif (Likely **Monument Extended**).
  - Body: Modern geometric sans-serif.
- **Hero Section**:
  - Background: Black.
  - Text: Large center-aligned white caps title.
  - Images: Three high-res images in a 3D/tilted perspective layout behind/around the text.
- **Navbar**:
  - Position: Fixed at the bottom center.
  - Style: Floating pill with light background, dark text.
- **Sections**:
  - **About**: Split layout (Light grey bg). Image left, text right. Lime green pill CTA.
  - **Services**: Floating "pill" cards with icons on a light gradient background.
  - **Portfolio**: Dark background. Huge bold caps titles for project categories.
  - **Brands**: Marquee/List of logos on dark background with "Marques mises en valeur" green pill tag.
  - **Stats**: Large colored cards (Orange, Blue, Green) with rounded corners and oversized numbers.
  - **FAQ**: Accordion-style on light/white background.
- **Footer**:
  - Background: Black with a white dashed grid overlay.
  - Elements: Massive "BREEZY RHINO" text. Large social icons (LinkedIn in Orange, FB in White, IG in Gradient).
  - CTAs: Large light blue pill for phone number, lime green pill for "Travailler ensemble".
- **Animations**:
  - Smooth scrolling (likely Lenis).
  - Fade-in and slide-up animations for text and cards on scroll.
  - Parallax on hero images.
  - Hover effects on pills: color inversion or subtle scaling.
